gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flickr.com/photos/ladyalec/8467293488/in/photolist-dUe6mL-z4TVvZ-o7Zi7U-FqFp9m-BdPRzP-JefMu6-wASGyS-q5rchj-GZwHqQ-6yqxkk-w7tgcp-9Cyfpe-4h2j4K-rjVfrt-227TrHe-SPUM23-vQuSrA-28gdzmN-p2gBCA-aosLDi-JJfNMy-bBVXww-bTFQgx-9MeVJL-pDckmw-p4mLzV-goxqsr-V4eKaJ-6rWmn5-3hoT2A-HnTGt5-dRbkGw-rrvKa7-f4bBBb-pRhNwH-a8Fy8R-znBYF7-ChuWom-J8syfN-pAaymK-GRytgb-2b2SzAt-bAqneN-KV9vAn-9N4etA-GUahg9-s9uUft-bpDxb3-NbzXdb-8M5MhH&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Lady Alec&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-vozrast field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Возраст:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/vozrast/5&quot;&gt;5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/vozrast/8&quot;&gt;8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/vozrast/10&quot;&gt;10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/vozrast/15&quot;&gt;15&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
